#

Classic New York Style Cheeseburger with Crispy Fried Onions

$18.99
950 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

BurgersAmerican CuisineComfort Food

Description

A classic cheeseburger topped with crispy fried onions and house-made pickles, paired with hand-cut fries and a refreshing cucumber mint salad.

Ingredients

  • Ground beef (80/20): 1 lb
  • Cheddar cheese: 4 slices
  • Burger buns: 4
  • Onion: 1 large, sliced
  • All-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • Buttermilk: 1 cup
  • Pickles: 1 cup, chopped
  • Potatoes: 4 large, for fries
  • Cucumber: 1 large, diced
  • Fresh mint: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
